Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.08,0:00:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,A curse corrodes Tomoe's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.88,0:00:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.65,0:00:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll travel back to when the curse was put 500 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.22,0:00:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be intruding.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.69,0:00:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The Tomoe of this era is a merciless supreme youkai.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.78,0:00:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The injured Tomoe, who was pursed by the villagers, was found by Nanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.40,0:00:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I know this child. Please help him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.68,0:00:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're hiding him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.58,0:00:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The woman, that you took in, picked up a wounded child last night, isn't it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.71,0:00:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! That fox is undoubtedly disguised as that child!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.81,0:00:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That woman is definitely a youkai's underling!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.19,0:00:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand over that woman and brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.58,0:00:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Yukiji-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.20,0:00:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami! Don't go out!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.12,0:00:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.00,0:00:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to Lady Yukiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.63,0:00:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I was the one who picked up that child who was clawed by the fox and had collapsed by the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.10,0:01:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,All of this is your fault for failing to hunt down that fox, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.52,0:01:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If you understand, then hurry up and go find that fox!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.63,0:01:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.93,0:01:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't hand over the brat obediently, then you'll be suspected.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.62,0:01:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you're actually an ally of the youkai.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.93,0:01:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I only want to protect you, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.45,0:01:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.34,0:01:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch me with your filthy hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.69,0:01:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If that kid sleeping inside really is the fox,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.78,0:01:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no need to hand him over to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.31,0:01:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tear him apart with my own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.78,0:01:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now, everyone. What's all this commotion for?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.58,0:01:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Youhei!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.36,0:01:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,A fox youkai has taken refuge in this house!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.32,0:01:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Youkai.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.51,0:01:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say such ridiculous things. There's no way something like that could be in our house.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.34,0:01:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Yukiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.10,0:01:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, father.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.64,0:01:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukiji is indeed lowborn, but I adopted her because of her beautiful face.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.83,0:02:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, she's getting proposals from nobles and rich men.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.21,0:02:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Youkai or whatnot, such strange rumors are intolerable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.94,0:02:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Her image before marriage is important after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.10,0:02:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No one in this house is on Tomoe's side, except me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.96,0:02:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The wound hasn't healed yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.72,0:02:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly what is this wound from?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.02,0:02:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, he won't last long.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.16,0:02:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm an outsider.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.17,0:02:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I shouldn't interfere with the past.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.94,0:02:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So please...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.66,0:02:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tomoe!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.18,0:02:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Open your eyes!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.95,0:02:52.40,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(280,130)\fade(500,500)}The Fox Falls in Love
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.83,0:02:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's hot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.54,0:02:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's hot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.33,0:02:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The wound's not healing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.52,0:03:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.94,0:03:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My body suddenly feels lighter.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.04,0:03:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Woman.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.24,0:03:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What did you do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.40,0:03:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Yukiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.53,0:03:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.70,0:03:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing. And where had you gone leaving this boy behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.20,0:03:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,For medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.67,0:03:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami has a very effective medicine for injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.74,0:03:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought of giving it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.92,0:03:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.79,0:03:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.24,0:03:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu-Yukiji-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.30,0:03:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomo-! I mean, how is Himetaro's condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.89,0:04:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, Fuuta is giving him the medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.19,0:04:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And you, why are you sitting in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.32,0:04:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay to watch over him from up close.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.62,0:04:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.31,0:04:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That kid would feel relieved if he sees you, won't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.06,0:04:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You know that kid, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.68,0:04:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.49,0:04:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't appear before him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.77,0:04:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because I can't meddle with the past.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.34,0:04:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I must go to the capital tomorrow on father's order.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.14,0:04:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll return after work's finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.39,0:04:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving Fuuta to help you, so rest assured.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.18,0:04:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing important.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.11,0:04:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like the landlord, who proposed marriage, wants to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.19,0:04:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,To accept his generous betrothal money, I'll dress myself as best as I can and go to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.01,0:04:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Are you getting married, Yukiji-san!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.40,0:04:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Only if he likes me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.10,0:05:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make such a worried face, Nanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.77,0:05:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...am not from this village.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.52,0:05:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,My hometown was attacked by a youkai one day, and everything burned to the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.88,0:05:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why, my parents, siblings and people related to me by blood, no one's in this world now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.44,0:05:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.16,0:05:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why, with you here, I feel the nostalgic warmth and affection of those bygone days.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.17,0:05:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.86,0:05:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,marrying is a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.83,0:05:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I... will create a family of my own blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.22,0:05:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.62,0:05:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My fever... is going down.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.82,0:05:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.40,0:06:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You've finally opened your eyes, Himetaro!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Good for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.60,0:06:04.80,overlap dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who's he?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.77,0:06:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The medicine really worked, right!? You must be hungry, right Himeta!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.54,0:06:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, your favourite *sasamochi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.54,0:06:12.07,sign2,,0,0,0,,{\an 8}*Note: sasamochi= rice cake wrapped in bamboo (sasa) leaves
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.41,0:06:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat this and wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.28,0:06:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll grill the fish I caught this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.78,0:06:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the woman who made these rice cakes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.32,0:06:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The woman who carried me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.72,0:06:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.86,0:06:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't tell him anything about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.36,0:06:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who saved you is the lady of this house, Yukiji-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.40,0:06:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The lady is quite busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.38,0:06:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You should rest now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.25,0:06:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...she was called Yukiji.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.02,0:06:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The wound that wouldn't heal...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.83,0:06:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...is gradually healing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.04,0:07:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just what kind of medicine did I take exactly?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.62,0:07:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Never mind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.39,0:07:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Until I've recovered completely, I shall remain here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.88,0:07:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And... that woman...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.53,0:07:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he's asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.68,0:07:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He just woke up today after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.33,0:07:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He won't recover so suddenly as he's not a youkai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.48,0:07:23.19,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(120,430)\fade(500,1500)}Pretends\N to sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.01,0:07:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.67,0:07:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Get well soon, Himeta.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.74,0:07:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,When you feel better, I'll take you to a good fishing spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.58,0:07:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukiji-sama's fishing skills are quite extraordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.57,0:07:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So get well soon. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.81,0:07:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If she knew that I'm a youkai, she wouldn't be able to stay this calm.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.33,0:07:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If she knew that I'm a youkai...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.02,0:07:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Rice cakes again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.29,0:07:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...that woman... what kind of face would she make?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.20,0:08:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a safe trip, Yukiji-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.12,0:08:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take care, my lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.14,0:08:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take care of the rest for me, Fuuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.78,0:08:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.36,0:08:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't leave in my absence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.04,0:08:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a promise, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.34,0:08:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.11,0:08:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He's asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.07,0:08:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.37,0:08:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He hasn't eaten the sasamochi, Fuuta-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.36,0:08:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it wasn't tasty?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.12,0:08:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I had made new ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.35,0:08:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.71,0:08:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Himeta was very full during the day, since he ate all the fish I had caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.12,0:08:50.80,overlap dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Himeta... do they mean me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.92,0:08:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,His wound is healing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.68,0:08:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.02,0:08:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Himeta is quite strong, even though he doesn't appear to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.80,0:09:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.81,0:09:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After my body recovers...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.66,0:09:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...I plan to abduct this woman.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.98,0:09:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But some thing is worrying me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.35,0:09:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why does she... only come every night when I'm asleep.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.93,0:09:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.87,0:09:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, he is asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.02,0:09:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.93,0:09:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What's this, so you {\i1}were{\i0} awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.46,0:09:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already time for kids to go to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.69,0:09:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, I'll change your bandage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.12,0:09:34.88,overlap dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.08,0:09:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Won't she come in?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.98,0:09:39.34,overlap dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll feel all better when you wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Boring...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.74,0:09:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When her hands touch me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.97,0:09:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...I feel so good too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.92,0:09:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.90,0:09:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Nanami!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.54,0:09:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuuta-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.60,0:09:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright? You look pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.66,0:10:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. My mind was just all fuzzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.51,0:10:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be tired, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.93,0:10:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Rest up for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.31,0:10:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already been 3 days since Yukiji-san left.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.04,0:10:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If everything goes well, she could return by tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.14,0:10:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Fuuta-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.90,0:10:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.79,0:10:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Himeta looks fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.99,0:10:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking about leaving this place tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.12,0:10:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.25,0:10:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukiji-sama told you to not leave, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.78,0:10:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.92,0:10:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for everything till now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.42,0:10:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for troubling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.06,0:10:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Why!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.63,0:10:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm an outsider.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.29,0:10:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I must not get in the way of Yukiji-san and others.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.31,0:10:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.90,0:10:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,A secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.10,0:10:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Your injury's all healed up, right Himeta?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.31,0:10:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why is it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.33,0:11:01.71,overlap dialogue,,0,0,0,,As promised, I'll take you to the fishing spot tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.10,0:11:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That woman didn't show herself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.70,0:11:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.04,0:11:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to Yukiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.14,0:11:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't address her that way! It's Lady Yukiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.97,0:11:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I never thought you'd be so foul mouthed. You're just Himetaro too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.79,0:11:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not Himetaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.84,0:11:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what {\i1}is{\i0} your name!!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.96,0:11:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Himetaro's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.14,0:11:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Yukiji is going to a rich man's place in the capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.48,0:11:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They are going to talk about their betrothal there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.56,0:11:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing, isn't it!? It's a wealthy household!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.63,0:11:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Yukiji will become the mistress of a much bigger house than this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.68,0:11:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Yukiji is the mistress of this house right now, but
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.94,0:11:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,long ago, because youkai set her village on fire, she went through a lot of pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.78,0:11:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why, I want lady Yukiji to be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.55,0:11:59.57,sign2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(420,120)\fade(100,0)}yawn
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.33,0:12:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Tch! This is why you're a brat! Go to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.68,0:12:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So she will belong to someone else?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.82,0:12:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Humans are fragile, break easily and become unable to move.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.98,0:12:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Being unable to move would mean the end of the game.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.57,0:12:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Once something is broken, it can't go back to the way it was.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.14,0:12:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If she's going to be by someone else's side,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.25,0:12:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll make her unable to move again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.28,0:12:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This game too... will then be over.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.30,0:12:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where is that woman?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.12,0:12:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rising and leaving the house at night, where is she going?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.28,0:12:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So be it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.63,0:12:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now then... how should I toy with her?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.38,0:13:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Woman,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.18,0:13:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}you have...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.77,0:13:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...caught my attention.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.51,0:13:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With that blood and flesh,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.80,0:13:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}entertain me till the end!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.75,0:13:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.66,0:13:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Humans are fragile, break easily and become unable to move.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.22,0:13:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Although I intended to toy with her....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.05,0:13:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...do I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.62,0:14:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...want this woman... not to die?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.62,0:14:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Just now, was there someone behind me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.20,0:14:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must hurry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.96,0:14:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My body hurts.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.21,0:14:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I remember this pain.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.58,0:14:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My body is starting to scream due to time travelling for this long.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.09,0:14:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The time for me to return to the present is approaching.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.47,0:14:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Like this, I can't return to the present without finding the fallen god.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.77,0:14:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is here alright?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.96,0:14:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if he's a fallen god or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.88,0:14:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,but I heard from my grandmother that a fiend lives in a pond at the foot of the mountain, up north of the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.24,0:15:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Long ago, it seems that babies were thrown as sacrifices there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.80,0:15:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't know whether the one Fuuta-kun talked about was the fallen god that I am searching for.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.52,0:15:06.47,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\frz 12\move(550,460,490,370)}Fallen God
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.98,0:15:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.60,0:15:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is the only way I can get a clue right now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.98,0:15:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please! Somehow... let my body hold on a bit longer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.00,0:15:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's dark.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.36,0:15:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Though it's still daytime too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.49,0:15:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A crying voice?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.06,0:15:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}From where?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.86,0:15:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts, it hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.09,0:15:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Fa-Fallen god!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.44,0:15:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the fallen god, aren't you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.34,0:15:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,On days when my back hurts a lot, I get in a bad mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.12,0:15:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't come over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.80,0:15:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't run away! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.98,0:16:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My body... won't listen to me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.13,0:16:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're{\i0} the one who nearly drowned yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.66,0:16:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not my fault, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.14,0:16:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Fallen god,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.82,0:16:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,please tell me the way to undo Tomoe's curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.46,0:16:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Turning youkai to humans!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.98,0:16:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You're saying I made such an arrangement!? That's too much! What an awful, wrong charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.00,0:16:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Not right now, I mean, in the near future.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.46,0:16:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just quietly living in this pond, is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.12,0:16:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,100 years ago, I ate human flesh and now am living as a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.92,0:16:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so rude to be referred to as a fallen god and such!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.42,0:16:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,To begin with, I don't have the power to convert youkai to humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.06,0:16:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As I thought,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.58,0:16:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}this wasn't the place where the fallen god was.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.00,0:16:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tomoe...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.08,0:17:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What should I do from now on?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.58,0:17:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a trick can't be performed by any god, much less a fallen god.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.52,0:17:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one being who can do it though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.09,0:17:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuromaro-dono from Mt. Ontake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.34,0:17:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He can change youkai into humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.40,0:17:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuromaro from Mt. Ontake?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.08,0:17:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a fallen god of old standing who was called a demon in ancient times.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.06,0:17:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,In terms of power, even Ookuninushi of Izumo couldn't stand his ground against this being.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.83,0:17:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Mt. Ontake? How can I meet Kuromaro!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.82,0:17:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to meet him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.14,0:17:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.56,0:17:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm losing the sensation in my legs!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.22,0:17:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to meet him, then I shall tell you how.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.62,0:17:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Really!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.58,0:17:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But, not just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.44,0:18:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If you give me all the peach pills you have, then I shall call on Kuromaro-dono here for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.23,0:18:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuromaro-dono will come immediately when he's called.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll come while being tailed by the grudges of this world, dying everything pitch black in his wake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.03,0:18:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If he arrives, this pond will be tainted with black and become uninhabitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.16,0:18:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Trading with your peach pills is not a bad idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.06,0:18:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you do, girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.91,0:18:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.37,0:18:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If doing this will help Tomoe...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.70,0:18:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Peach pills!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.53,0:18:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,With this my back pain will disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.37,0:18:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, call Kuromaro....
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.83,0:18:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuromaro-donooooooo!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.90,0:18:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I've called him, human goddess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.73,0:18:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait a minute! Where is Kuromaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.59,0:18:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so anxious. My voice has definitely reached Mt. Ontake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.68,0:19:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.08,0:19:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The northern sky is darkening.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.78,0:19:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.04,0:19:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.72,0:19:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuromaro-dono will come immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.37,0:19:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He has a lot of spare time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.00,0:19:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's coming.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.03,0:19:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's always yearning for company.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.34,0:19:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A sinister black.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.21,0:19:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a lonely being.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.82,0:19:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Beings of the pond,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.92,0:19:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,do you have any business with this Kuromaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.15,0:19:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My hands are numb.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.44,0:19:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.93,0:19:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just a bit more!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.95,0:19:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just a bit more...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.44,0:19:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can grasp the key to undo the curse!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.58,0:19:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In just a while, I'll be able to save Tomoe!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.20,0:19:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's okay if my body becomes useless!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.71,0:19:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If this helps Tomoe...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.16,0:19:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My voice... won't come out!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.46,0:19:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.12,0:20:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.21,0:20:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My body's being pulled!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.45,0:20:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Time's up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.00,0:20:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Return to the present.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.46,0:20:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait! Just a bit more!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.46,0:20:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a bit more and I can save Tomoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.00,0:20:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,In just a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.54,0:20:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Nanami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.24,0:20:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That was one long time-travel, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.83,0:20:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikage-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.31,0:20:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, don't move so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.23,0:20:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Time travel essentially takes a huge toll on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.86,0:20:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Mikage shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.70,0:20:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been sleeping here all night since your return.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.23,0:20:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoe is still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.52,0:20:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.36,0:20:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Rest well till your strength returns.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.76,0:20:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikage-san, you brought me back, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.30,0:20:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.90,0:20:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,In just a bit, I would have been able to talk to the fallen god too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.74,0:20:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I could have saved Tomoe too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.71,0:21:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I had left you just like that, your body-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.41,0:21:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care about my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.84,0:21:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go back once more to the past, right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.86,0:21:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible with your body like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.38,0:21:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I... will save Tomoe all by myself!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.54,0:21:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.21,0:21:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.14,0:21:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like you care for Tomoe,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.73,0:21:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoe, Mizuki and everyone else care about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.00,0:21:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why, you should take better care of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.51,0:21:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't shoulder everything alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.16,0:21:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if everyone is far away, they'll be watching over you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.48,0:21:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mikage-san's gentle voice...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.60,0:21:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...is soothing my strained feelings.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.74,0:21:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,To go back to the past, you must prepare your physical condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.95,0:21:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,First, let's replenish your energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.71,0:22:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you hungry yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.42,0:22:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.63,0:22:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, everyone is putting your share of ingredients.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.00,0:22:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.47,0:22:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.57,0:22:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-sama!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.11,0:22:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha? What's happening everyone? Gathering around like that...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.82,0:22:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, everyone barged in, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.82,0:22:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-sama!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.24,0:22:28.86,overlap dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onikiri-kun! Kotetsu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.08,0:22:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-chaaan!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.90,0:22:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Nanami-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.48,0:22:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, Mikage-san took me back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.64,0:22:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Mizuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.93,0:22:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I rushed here on hearing that your familiar was in grave danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.00,0:22:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy should die once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.28,0:22:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's anything we could do to help, please tell us, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.91,0:22:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuu-ou, Kamehime-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.22,0:22:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.82,0:22:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that you're not feeling well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.24,0:22:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an excellent restorative handed down in my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.49,0:22:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Kurama...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.05,0:23:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow the directions for your recovery and take your medicine properly. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.28,0:23:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And here's a souvenir from Nezumi Land.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.12,0:23:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Kota chose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.45,0:23:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,They're sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.82,0:23:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So you {\i1}did{\i0} go to Nemzumi Land.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.25,0:23:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So? Where's that damn fox right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.27,0:23:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Tomoe's in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.98,0:23:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey fox! So you're dying? How disappointing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.20,0:23:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Repay your debt to me first, then die!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.74,0:23:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear, please behave yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.30,0:23:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, it's just as Ryuu-ou says.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.77,0:23:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't cause hardship for Nanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.62,0:23:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,A familiar causing trouble for their master is the worst, Tomoe-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.78,0:23:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's correct. Hurry and come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.05,0:23:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. I need you to transform me into a human once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.68,0:23:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go to another of those humans' theme park with Kota.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.78,0:23:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi-Himemiko-chan...!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.34,0:23:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how it is, so I'm sorry, but please once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.63,0:24:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.60,0:24:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wasn't alone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.63,0:24:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tomoe and I... we both have a home where everyone gathers.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.02,0:24:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! I'll eat a lot to be able to rush back to the past!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.59,0:24:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me some protein!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.98,0:24:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Here's Nanami-chan's share.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.30,0:24:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't any meat in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.10,0:24:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why, return to us soon, okay, Tomoe?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.56,0:24:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lately...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.13,0:24:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...I don't have the will to do anything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.09,0:24:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why is that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.20,0:24:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I nearly died, or was it that I was reborn?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.32,0:24:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Since that day,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.52,0:24:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}did something happen to me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.86,0:25:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unlike me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.72,0:25:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This plight is unlike me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.41,0:25:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Akura-ou! Where are you, Akura-ou!?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.07,0:25:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's play!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.50,0:25:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo, brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.14,0:25:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.12,0:25:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What's alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.48,0:25:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that furball over there,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.19,0:25:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,said that you are lovesick.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.95,0:25:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, in love!?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.85,0:25:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.52,0:25:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I laughed hard on hearing that too!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.84,0:25:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I told him,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.65,0:25:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,my brother's not an idiot who'd be infatuated by a human woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.35,0:25:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But still, you're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.17,0:25:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I came across something interesting outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.64,0:25:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like a young woman, living in a small village by the river, will be having a bridal procession soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.67,0:25:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, furball heard them say that she's a great beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.82,0:26:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Her name was... Yukiji, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.94,0:26:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There aren't many beauties named Yukiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.77,0:26:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If she's really that beautiful, I thought I'd like to take a look myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.83,0:26:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a while ago, I gave out an order to a subordinate on the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.46,0:26:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I told him to pull out the most well dressed bride from that procession and bring her to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.75,0:26:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a boring game.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.60,0:26:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So? When's the bridal procession?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.30,0:26:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's after 3 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.96,0:26:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.02,0:26:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to see her?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.72,0:26:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not really interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.59,0:26:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you don't mind me doing whatever I want, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.22,0:26:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.33,0:26:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! I'm leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.02,0:26:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To the past!{\i0}
