Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.41,0:28:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami travelled into the past for the second time.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.61,0:28:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukiji will be marrying a lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.66,0:28:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,However, a youkai targeting Yukiji's life appears.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.46,0:28:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So, to keep her safe, Nanami suggests to be Yukiji's substitute.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.19,0:28:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, The God becomes a bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.90,0:28:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What's Tomoe's true intention?